      "8-stage B2B buying process (not all stages apply to every purchase)",
      "3 buying situations: straight rebuy, modified rebuy, new task",
      "Key Account Management: dedicated resources for top customers (80/20 rule)",
      "Derived demand: B2B demand depends on end-consumer demand"
