      "Positioning is about the consumer's MIND, not the product itself",
      "Perceptual maps visualize brand positions based on consumer perceptions",
      "Brand laddering: Attribute → Functional → Emotional → Value",
      "Golden Circle: WHY → HOW → WHAT (communicate purpose first)",
      "USP: the single compelling reason to choose your brand over competitors",
      "5 differentiation sources: product, services, channel, people, image",
      "7 criteria for sustainable competitive advantage"
